data.description: Charming, well loved and cared for hard to find 4 bedroom bungalow just a short 1 block walk to Lake Sacajawea! Open and bright living/dining room with high ceilings and wonderful custom touches. Enjoy the remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances and huge custom walk-in pantry! The back patio is perfect for warm summer night dinners and entertaining. The yard is fully fenced with an abundance of gorgeous perennials. Large detached 1 car garage/workshop along with tool shed! New 200 amp electric panel was just installed. Don't miss this hard-to-find gem! Call your favorite Realtor and schedule your private showing today!
